;THE NUMBERING OF THE SECONDARY STRUCTURE ELEMENTS HAS
SYMBOLS AFTER SOYBEAN LIPOXYGENASE L1 AS IN PDB ENTRY 2SBL
(BOYINGTON ET AL., 1993, SCIENCE, 260, 1482-1486).
THERE ARE SOME KINKS IN 3 HELICES: H2 - AT 283,
H9 - AT 521-522, H18 - AT 706, 714-715.
;
_pdbx_entry_details.source_details           ? 
_pdbx_entry_details.nonpolymer_details       
;THE IRON BINDING SITE CONSISTS OF HIS 518, HIS 523, HIS 709
AND ILE 857(C-TERMINAL) THAT ARE COVALENTLY BOUND TO IRON
FE 858, WHILE ASN 713 AND H2O 901 ARE IN A DISTANCE GREATER
THAN THE SUM OF THE VAN DER WAALS RADII.
;
_pdbx_entry_details.sequence_details         ? 
_pdbx_entry_details.has_ligand_of_interest   ? 
